                <note rend="inline" type="source">851.4061/89: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Herrick</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-05-04T18:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 4, 1928—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>124. Your 111, May 2, 3 p.m. Department cordially approves such informal
                    conciliatory efforts by Embassy.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
